programme.sub-title: Key Largo, Florida Keys: Pounding the Patches
programme.desc: Some of the easiest and most enjoyable fishing throughout the Florida Keys is on the patchreefs. With the MARC VI's live wells loaded with pilchards and ballyhoo, Poveromo and Captain Kevin Jeffries find themselves probing the patches off Key Largo.
